Hello!
Icarus does not support associative arrays, for example  logic [4:0] a [*];
When I try to buit it

```verilog
module tb;
logic [4:0] a[*];
initial begin
    a[10] = 1'b1;
    a[20] = 1'b0;
    $display(a);
end
endmodule
````

I have got:
iverilog -Wall -g2012  -Y .sv -y . -o tb tb.sv
tb.sv:2: syntax error
tb.sv:1: error: syntax error in variable list.

code_blocks:
